Created Model-driven APP via Make Power Apps(https://make.powerapps.com/).
Connected the APP with CDS database, this also enabled the connection between the Canvas and Model-driven APPs.
Created business process flow using Power Automate(https://us.flow.microsoft.com/)
Configure the CDS database table to capture new information needed for the precurement process.
The Model-driven APP is to complete the back-office process of managing procurement, setting up device and distribution.